{"tid":17303,"cid":28,"subCid":0,"title":"究竟啲5p仔喺邊到死出黎","createTime":"2016-12-01T18:59:17.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-09T13:44:26.000Z","uid":6097,"like":92,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3249f69b83f69377e88b84f1d3def5163046c1de","tid":17303,"uid":6097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T18:59:17.000Z","msg":"有無人發覺5p情況日益嚴重"},{"pid":"2f51120ea47705c510bd6050bafb1dd9bdf72111","tid":17303,"uid":6097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T19:12:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有無人發覺5p情況日益嚴重</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n屌未出哂<br />\n差唔多個個post都有人吾系甘牙<br />\nDeep web個post個5p樓主直情打埋挽<br />\n真係挽你老母個臭化閪咩<br />\n字都唔撚識打學咩人上討論區<br />\n<br />\n係咪覺得有個AC好威威 終於有得叫「高登仔」<br />\n但真係狗改不了吃屎<br />\n情況就好似支那蝗拎香港身分證咁 <br />\n啲行為文化唔跟香港 無人會當你係香港人<br />\n又內至外都仍然係一件支那蝗 唔受本地人所接納<br />\n<br />\n我知未必要跟高登規矩 但係打返正字都係一份尊重<br />\n吾系甘牙真係篤眼篤鼻 都唔知你講乜春<br />\n無讀過書?淨係識打同音字?<br />\n最恐怖係屌佢地既人少咗好多 <br />\n我唔想我鐘意既論壇變成U汪/香討之流<br />\n<br />\n所以麻煩大家真係要見一次屌一次<br />\n維護我哋既正字文化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b8e13b12953cb2c6ef081ea0efb66dd7d908602","tid":17303,"uid":16016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T19:14:21.000Z","msg":"啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb52dbee32ffb7434fd5ac6dc57f9ee9a09ff6da","tid":17303,"uid":6097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T19:14:24.000Z","msg":"自推會唔會入黑洞架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f9146b7f0f6ec4d383c8ea70b6baf141e0f8d9c","tid":17303,"uid":27477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T19:16:27.000Z","msg":"正常post冇人理 on9 5p post就一大堆人討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37933174481943c760388c5beaf04435b0b28b28","tid":17303,"uid":6097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-